data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled 5-bedroom, 3-bath manufactured home. Step inside and be captivated by its modern charm and inviting atmosphere. The interior has been thoughtfully renovated with exquisite details throughout. Located in Willcox this property has beautiful views! This home is fully equipped with a nice split layout floor plan, freshly interior paint, newer waterproof laminate floors throughout and offers open concept living room and dining perfect for entertaining. The kitchen features plenty of cabinetry with knobs and pulls, laminate counter-tops, stainless steel sink, and adjacent breakfast nook! All appliances will convey including washer and dryer! Laundry room is right off the kitchen. Principal suite features a beautiful barn door, double sink split vanity with with a nice walk in shower and corner tub. A Jack and Jill bathroom divides the spacious guest rooms. This property received some updating such as the electrical, full repipe plumbing throughout & brand new HVAC system with metal ducts underneath home. Situated on 1.25 acre lot, this fully enclosed property has plenty of room for you to create the backyard of your dreams!
